        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 7 at 7:38PM CDT until June 7 at 8:00PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 738 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 15 miles northeast
of Romero, or 18 miles southwest of Dalhart, moving southeast at 40
mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible. Hail
damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Romero.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
